videos.description: Iowa State's Cameron Lard drives to the basket and goes up for the layup but Sagaba Konate grabs it out of mid-air.
videos.headline: Konate snags shot out of mid-air

videos.description: After an Iowa State miss, Jevon Carter grabs a rebound and drives the length of the court to finish strong with a layup and the foul.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Carter extends for and-1

videos.description: After a Jevon Carter missed 3-pointer, Esa Ahmad grabs the offensive rebound and slams it down.
videos.headline: Ahmad redeems WVU miss with monster slam

videos.description: Zoran Talley Jr. drives and puts the moves on West Virginia defenders before extending and completing the and-1.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Talley Jr. spins and finishes for and-1

videos.description: After a defensive stop, Iowa State's Lindell Wigginton takes the pass off the fast break and Eurosteps for two points
videos.headline: Wigginton Eurosteps for an Iowa State floater

videos.description: West Virginia's Daxter Miles Jr. steals a bad Iowa State pass and plays it up to Esa Ahmad who throws it down.
videos.headline: Ahmad's fast-break dunk helps extend WVU lead

videos.description: Jevon Carter throws a deep pass to Daxter Miles Jr. who impressively saves it from going out of bounds while passing it backwards to Lamont West who sinks the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Miles Jr.'s incredible save leads to and-1
